            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Vision:</strong> A world where every family has access to basic needs and opportunities for growth.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Mission:</strong> To provide integrated support for vulnerable families through housing, food security, education, healthcare, and community empowerment.
                </li>
            </ul>
