        <section class="core-components">
            <h2 class="section-title">üèóÔ∏è Core Components of the Platform</h2>

            <div class="component-item">
                <h3>1. Housing Support</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Partner with local housing authorities and NGOs to provide temporary shelters and long-term affordable housing.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Create a database of available housing resources and connect families with landlords willing to offer subsidized rent.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Offer micro-grants for emergency housing needs.
                    </li>

                <h3>2. Food Security</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Build partnerships with food banks, grocery stores, and restaurants for donations.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Develop a community kitchen program where volunteers prepare meals for families.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Implement a digital voucher system for families to access food at partner stores.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h3>3. Education</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Provide scholarship for childer and adults to continue schooling
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Offer free online courses and tutoring programs.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Partner with schools and universities for donated supplies, mentorship and training.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h3>4. Medical Assistance</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Collaborate with hospitals and clinics to provide free or subsidized healthcare.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Organize medical camps for preventive care and screenings.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Provide access to mental health counseling and wellness programs.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h3>5. Other Essential Support</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Job placement and vocational training programs.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Legal aid for families facing eviction or immigration challenges.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Childcare services to support working parents.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            </section>
